AXIA — Futuristic Digital Agency Landing Page

AXIA is a premium, interactive landing page for a digital agency that helps startups and small businesses launch modern, high-quality websites. Built with React, Tailwind CSS, and Framer Motion, it showcases glassmorphism UI, animated gradients, floating particles, smooth micro-interactions, and interactive pricing cards.

Features

Futuristic UI: Glass cards, neon accents, and floating particles

Interactive Pricing: Multi-option CTA buttons (Gmail, Outlook, LinkedIn)

Tech Stack Showcase: Clients can choose their preferred languages

Smooth Animations: Hover effects, scroll reveal, and transitions

Responsive Design: Optimized for desktop and mobile
